org.anchoranalysis.plugin.annotation.bean.comparison.assigner

Class FeatureCostAssigner

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<AnnotationComparisonAssigner<T>>
      • AnnotationComparisonAssigner<AssignmentOverlapFromPairs>
        • FeatureCostAssigner

  • public class FeatureCostAssigner
extends AnnotationComparisonAssigner<AssignmentOverlapFromPairs>
    Assigns an objects from one set of objects to another based upon a cost (degree of overlap).

    This is a form of bipartite matching.

    The following outputs are produced:

    Output NameDefault?Description
    costMatrixnoa CSV file showing a matrix of costs calculated for the objects.
    Author:
    Owen Feehan
